---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { SITE } from '../consts';
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="How GetInsuredBC collects, uses, and protects your personal information.">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-5 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl text-primary">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <div class="prose-content mt-8 text-muted-foreground">
      <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>At GetInsuredBC, we collect information that you provide directly to us when you use our services, including when you fill out our insurance assessment, contact us, or interact with our website. This may include personal identification information (name, email address, phone number), insurance-related information (coverage needs, health information, financial details), and device and usage information (IP address, browser type, pages visited).</p>

      <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>We use the information we collect to provide, maintain, and improve our services; process your insurance requests and applications; communicate with you about our services, offers, and updates; analyze usage patterns to enhance your experience; and comply with legal obligations and protect against fraud.</p>

      <h2>3. Information Sharing</h2>
      <p>We may share your information with insurance providers and underwriters to process your requests, and with service providers who assist in our operations or legal authorities when required by law. We do not sell your personal information to third parties.</p>

      <h2>4. Data Security</h2>
      <p>We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal information against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. However, no method of transmission over the Internet is 100% secure.</p>

      <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
      <p>You have the right to access the personal information we hold about you, request correction of inaccurate information, request deletion of your personal information, opt out of marketing communications, and lodge a complaint with a supervisory authority.</p>

      <h2>6. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
      <p>We use cookies and similar technologies to understand how our website is used. You can instruct your browser to refuse cookies or to indicate when a cookie is being sent.</p>

      <h2>7. Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>Our services are not directed to individuals under the age of 18, and we do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 18.</p>

      <h2>8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will post the new policy on this page and update the date below.</p>

      <h2>9. Contact Us</h2>
      <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, contact us at <a href={`mailto:${SITE.email}`}>{SITE.email}</a>, or write to {SITE.address.street}, {SITE.address.city}, {SITE.address.region}.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
